metadata.name: PirateVerse
metadata.description: PirateVerse is a whole new pirate world which you can experience. PirateVerse - Ships is the first NFT Collection of PirateVerse consisting of 10,000 unique ships on Ethereum Blockchain. Take your ship on a voyage and feel the fantasy of pirate's life. Explore the islands filled with treasure and mysterious creatures and fight against other pirates to test your mettle. Which Ship will you get?
